{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1122,"text":"I am sorry I cannot show you my face,"},{"time":5119,"text":"because if I do, the bad guys will come for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10205,"text":"My journey started 14 years ago."},{"time":14293,"text":"I was a young reporter. I had just come out of college."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18705,"text":"Then I got a scoop."},{"time":21407,"text":"The scoop was quite a very simple story."},{"time":24826,"text":"Police officers were taking bribes"},{"time":27430,"text":"from hawkers who were hawking on the streets."},{"time":30966,"text":"As a young reporter, I thought that I should do it"},{"time":33768,"text":"in a different way, so that it has a maximum impact,"},{"time":37937,"text":"since everybody knew that it was happening,"},{"time":39825,"text":"and yet there was nothing that was keeping it out of the system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43394,"text":"So I decided to go there"},{"time":45629,"text":"and act as a seller."},{"time":49594,"text":"As part of selling, I was able to document"},{"time":52847,"text":"the hard core evidence."},{"time":55639,"text":"The impact was great."},{"time":58161,"text":"It was fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60722,"text":"This was what many call immersion journalism,"},{"time":64452,"text":"or undercover journalism."},{"time":67021,"text":"I am an undercover journalist."},{"time":71269,"text":"My journalism is hinged on three basic principles:"},{"time":75990,"text":"naming, shaming and jailing."},{"time":80790,"text":"Journalism is about results."},{"time":82660,"text":"It's about affecting your community or your society"},{"time":86399,"text":"in the most progressive way."},{"time":89036,"text":"I have worked on this for over 14 years,"},{"time":93594,"text":"and I can tell you, the results are very good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96826,"text":"One story that comes to mind"},{"time":99057,"text":"in my undercover pieces"},{"time":101201,"text":"is \"Spirit Child.\""},{"time":103412,"text":"It was about children who were born with deformities,"},{"time":107488,"text":"and their parents felt that once they were born"},{"time":110233,"text":"with those deformities,"},{"time":111922,"text":"they were not good enough to live in the society,"},{"time":114045,"text":"so they were given some concoction to take"},{"time":117153,"text":"and as a result they died."},{"time":119730,"text":"So I built a prosthetic baby,"},{"time":122547,"text":"and I went into the village,"},{"time":124697,"text":"pretended as though this baby had been born"},{"time":128845,"text":"with a deformity, and here was the guys who do the killing."},{"time":132932,"text":"They got themselves ready."},{"time":135507,"text":"In their bids to kill, I got the police on standby,"},{"time":139093,"text":"and they came that fateful morning"},{"time":141633,"text":"to come and kill the child."},{"time":144469,"text":"I recall how they were seriously boiling the concoction."},{"time":148488,"text":"They put it on fire. It was boiling hot,"},{"time":151408,"text":"getting ready to give to the kids."},{"time":153880,"text":"Whilst this was going on, the police I had alerted,"},{"time":155855,"text":"they were on standby,"},{"time":158528,"text":"and just as the concoction was ready,"},{"time":161764,"text":"and they were about to give it to the kids,"},{"time":164864,"text":"I phoned the police,"},{"time":166813,"text":"and fortunately they came and busted them."},{"time":170982,"text":"As I speak now, they are before the courts."},{"time":173934,"text":"Don't forget the key principles:"},{"time":175748,"text":"naming, shaming and jailing."},{"time":178574,"text":"The court process is taking place,"},{"time":180587,"text":"and I'm very sure at the end of the day"},{"time":182670,"text":"we will find them, and we will put them"},{"time":185119,"text":"where they belong too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187862,"text":"Another key story that comes to mind,"},{"time":190550,"text":"which relates to this spirit child phenomenon,"},{"time":194897,"text":"is \"The Spell of the Albinos.\""},{"time":200373,"text":"I'm sure most of you may have heard, in Tanzania,"},{"time":203864,"text":"children who are born with albinism"},{"time":206240,"text":"are sometimes considered as being unfit"},{"time":210293,"text":"to live in society."},{"time":212992,"text":"Their bodies are chopped up with machetes"},{"time":216880,"text":"and are supposed to be used for some concoctions"},{"time":220208,"text":"or some potions for people to get money --"},{"time":223090,"text":"or so many, many stories people would tell about it."},{"time":226885,"text":"It was time to go undercover again."},{"time":229441,"text":"So I went undercover as a man who was interested"},{"time":232890,"text":"in this particular business, of course."},{"time":235023,"text":"Again, a prosthetic arm was built."},{"time":237593,"text":"For the first time, I filmed on hidden camera"},{"time":241172,"text":"the guys who do this, and they were ready to buy the arm"},{"time":245916,"text":"and they were ready to use it to prepare"},{"time":248066,"text":"those potions for people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251730,"text":"I am glad today the Tanzanian government has taken action,"},{"time":255306,"text":"but the key issue is that the Tanzanian government"},{"time":258448,"text":"could only take action because the evidence was available."},{"time":262637,"text":"My journalism is about hard core evidence."},{"time":266532,"text":"If I say you have stolen, I show you the evidence"},{"time":268931,"text":"that you have stolen."},{"time":270434,"text":"I show you how you stole it"},{"time":272751,"text":"and when, or what you used"},{"time":274471,"text":"what you had stolen to do."},{"time":276739,"text":"What is the essence of journalism if it doesn't benefit society?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281309,"text":"My kind of journalism is a product"},{"time":283753,"text":"of my society."},{"time":287170,"text":"I know that sometimes"},{"time":290348,"text":"people have their own criticisms"},{"time":294020,"text":"about undercover journalism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297508,"text":"(Video) Official: He brought out some money from his pockets"},{"time":301686,"text":"and put it on the table,"},{"time":304640,"text":"so that we should not be afraid."},{"time":307955,"text":"He wants to bring the cocoa and send it to Cote d'Ivoire."},{"time":313738,"text":"So with my hidden intention, I kept quiet."},{"time":317426,"text":"I didn't utter a word."},{"time":319816,"text":"But my colleagues didn't know."},{"time":321674,"text":"So after collecting the money,"},{"time":324895,"text":"when he left, we were waiting for him to bring the goods."},{"time":328023,"text":"Immediately after he left, I told my colleagues that"},{"time":331458,"text":"since I was the leader of the group,"},{"time":332975,"text":"I told my colleagues that if they come,"},{"time":335972,"text":"we will arrest them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337273,"text":"Second official: I don't even know the place called [unclear]."},{"time":341500,"text":"I've never stepped there before."},{"time":343084,"text":"So I'm surprised."},{"time":344051,"text":"You see a hand counting money just in front of me."},{"time":349865,"text":"The next moment, you see the money in my hands,"},{"time":353209,"text":"counting, whereas I have not come into contact with anybody."},{"time":356530,"text":"I have not done any business with anybody."},{"time":359095,"text":"Reporter: When Metro News contacted investigative reporter"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361435,"text":"Anas Aremeyaw Anas for his reaction,"},{"time":363616,"text":"he just smiled and gave this video extract"},{"time":366490,"text":"he did not use in the documentary recently shown onscreen."},{"time":371245,"text":"The officer who earlier denied involvement"},{"time":373594,"text":"pecks a calculator to compute the amount of money"},{"time":376656,"text":"they will charge on the cocoa to be smuggled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381248,"text":"Anas Aremeyaw Anas: This was another story on anticorruption."},{"time":383858,"text":"And here was him, denying."},{"time":385750,"text":"But you see, when you have the hard core evidence,"},{"time":387711,"text":"you are able to affect society."},{"time":391071,"text":"Sometimes these are some of the headlines that come. (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":393378,"text":"[I will curse Anas to death]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":395144,"text":"[Anas Lies]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397508,"text":"[Alarm Blows Over Anas' News for Cash Video]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400865,"text":"[Agenda Against Top CEPS Officials Exposed]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":403718,"text":"[Anas Operates with Invisible Powers?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406920,"text":"[Gov't Wobbles Over Anas Video]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":409498,"text":"[Hunting the Hunter]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412306,"text":"[Anas 'Bribe' Men in Court]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":415041,"text":"[15 Heads Roll Over Anas Tape]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":419165,"text":"[Finance Minister Backs Anas]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423126,"text":"[11 Given Queries Over Anas' Story]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":426254,"text":"[GJA Stands By Anas]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429641,"text":"[Prez. Mills Storms Tema Harbour Over Anas Video]"},{"time":433406,"text":"[\"Late Prof. John Evans Atta Mills: Former president of Ghana\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":437121,"text":"John Evans Atta Mills: What Anas says"},{"time":439298,"text":"is not something which is unknown to many of us,"},{"time":443204,"text":"but please, those of you who are agents,"},{"time":447308,"text":"and who are leading the customs officers into temptation,"},{"time":451891,"text":"I'm telling you, Ghana is not going to say"},{"time":456244,"text":"any good things to you about this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458843,"text":"AAA: That was my president."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461186,"text":"I thought that I couldn't come here"},{"time":463546,"text":"without giving you something special."},{"time":466026,"text":"I have a piece, and I'm excited that"},{"time":469517,"text":"I'm sharing it for the first time with you here."},{"time":473599,"text":"I have been undercover in the prisons."},{"time":477705,"text":"I have been there for a long time."},{"time":481891,"text":"And I can tell you, what I saw is not nice."},{"time":486920,"text":"But again, I can only affect society"},{"time":489821,"text":"and affect government if I bring out the hard core evidence."},{"time":493397,"text":"Many times, the prison authorities have denied"},{"time":496769,"text":"ever having issues of drug abuse,"},{"time":499317,"text":"issues of sodomy, so many issues they would deny"},{"time":503297,"text":"that it ever happens."},{"time":504747,"text":"How can you obtain the hard core evidence?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":508111,"text":"So I was in the prison. [\"Nsawan Prison\"]"},{"time":512011,"text":"Now, what you are seeing is a pile of dead bodies."},{"time":516197,"text":"Now, I happen to have followed one of my inmates,"},{"time":519267,"text":"one of my friends, from his sick bed till death,"},{"time":523823,"text":"and I can tell you it was not a nice thing at all."},{"time":527464,"text":"There were issues of bad food being served"},{"time":530546,"text":"as I recall that some of the food I ate"},{"time":535456,"text":"is just not good for a human being."},{"time":539717,"text":"Toilet facilities: very bad."},{"time":543868,"text":"I mean, you had to queue to get proper toilets to attend --"},{"time":548292,"text":"and that's what I call proper,"},{"time":551008,"text":"when four of us are on a manhole."},{"time":554417,"text":"It is something that if you narrate it to somebody,"},{"time":558157,"text":"the person wouldn't believe it."},{"time":559991,"text":"The only way that you can let the person believe"},{"time":562197,"text":"is when you show hard core evidence."},{"time":564309,"text":"Of course, drugs were abundant."},{"time":567437,"text":"It was easier to get cannabis, heroin and cocaine,"},{"time":570182,"text":"faster even, in the prison than outside the prison."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573885,"text":"Evil in the society is an extreme disease."},{"time":578596,"text":"If you have extreme diseases,"},{"time":580518,"text":"you need to get extreme remedies."},{"time":583445,"text":"My kind of journalism might not fit in other continents"},{"time":586179,"text":"or other countries,"},{"time":587861,"text":"but I can tell you, it works in my part of the continent"},{"time":591309,"text":"of Africa, because usually, when people talk"},{"time":593517,"text":"about corruption, they ask, \"Where is the evidence?"},{"time":596242,"text":"Show me the evidence.\""},{"time":597423,"text":"I say, \"This is the evidence.\""},{"time":599328,"text":"And that has aided in me putting a lot of people behind bars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604209,"text":"You see, we on the continent are able"},{"time":607729,"text":"to tell the story better because we face the conditions"},{"time":610313,"text":"and we see the conditions."},{"time":612713,"text":"That is why I was particularly excited"},{"time":614500,"text":"when we launched our \"Africa Investigates\" series"},{"time":616880,"text":"where we investigated a lot of African countries."},{"time":620081,"text":"As a result of the success of the \"Africa Investigates\" series,"},{"time":623732,"text":"we are moving on to World Investigates."},{"time":626270,"text":"By the end of it, a lot more bad guys"},{"time":628913,"text":"on our continent will be put behind bars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632543,"text":"This will not stop."},{"time":634170,"text":"I'm going to carry on with this kind of journalism,"},{"time":637097,"text":"because I know that when evil men destroy,"},{"time":640525,"text":"good men must build and bind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642513,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643786,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":653323,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thank you. Thank you."},{"time":655021,"text":"I have some questions for you."},{"time":657269,"text":"How did you end up in jail? This was just a few weeks ago, I believe, yeah?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":661499,"text":"AAA: Sure. You know, undercover is all about"},{"time":663714,"text":"setting the priorities right, so we got people"},{"time":666580,"text":"to take me to court."},{"time":668418,"text":"So I went through the very legal process,"},{"time":670634,"text":"because at the end of the day, the prison authorities"},{"time":672858,"text":"want to check whether indeed you have been there or not,"},{"time":675474,"text":"and that's how I got in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677488,"text":"CA: So someone sued you in court,"},{"time":679266,"text":"and they took you there, and you were in remand custody"},{"time":682073,"text":"for part of it, and you did that deliberately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684514,"text":"AAA: Yes, yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686205,"text":"CA: Talk to me just about fear"},{"time":689368,"text":"and how you manage that,"},{"time":691177,"text":"because you're regularly putting your life at risk."},{"time":693810,"text":"How do you do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":695373,"text":"AAA: You see, undercover is always a last resort."},{"time":698563,"text":"Before we go undercover, we follow the rules."},{"time":700777,"text":"And I'm only comfortable and I'm purged of fear"},{"time":703847,"text":"whenever I am sure that all the steps"},{"time":706327,"text":"have been taken. I don't do it alone. I have a backup team"},{"time":709535,"text":"who help ensure that the safety and all the systems"},{"time":712900,"text":"are put in place, but you've got to take"},{"time":714845,"text":"very intelligent decisions whenever they are happening."},{"time":717596,"text":"If you don't, you will end up losing your life."},{"time":720212,"text":"So yes, when the backup systems are put in place,"},{"time":722716,"text":"I'm okay, I go in. Risky, yes,"},{"time":724804,"text":"but it's a hazard of a profession."},{"time":727460,"text":"I mean, everybody has their hazard."},{"time":729013,"text":"And once you say that is yours,"},{"time":730946,"text":"you've got to take it, as and when it comes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733254,"text":"CA: Well, you're an amazing human and you've done amazing work"},{"time":735945,"text":"and you've taught us a story"},{"time":737215,"text":"like no story I think any of us have heard before."},{"time":740462,"text":"And we're appreciative. We salute you. Thank you so much, Anas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":744306,"text":"AAA: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":745430,"text":"CA: Thank you. Stay safe. (Applause)"}]}]}